{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香跳入高墙后的庭园，在花林小轩中遇到一位冷艳如寒月梅花的白衣女子。女子态度淡然，邀他喝茶，甚至将自己喝过的茶递给他。楚留香问出她是策划暗杀的主谋，她坦然承认。楚留香追问艾青姐妹下落，女子不答，反以床上为由邀他入罗帐。楚留香发现她双手完美无瑕，确定她未练过武功。正当女子让他抱到床上、楚留香犹豫追问幕后主使时，窗外有人高喊捉采花贼。女子不惊不慌，问他究竟是君子还是聪明人。楚留香自嘲是傻子，悄然离去。女子独自在黑暗中流下眼泪。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "请坐",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这杯茶我刚喝过，你嫌不嫌脏？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "多谢",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这儿只有一个茶杯，因为从来都没有客人来过。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "我也不能算你的客人",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你却是来找我的",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "也许是",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "也许？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "现在我只能这样说，因为我还不知道你是不是我要找的人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要找的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "有个人好像一定要我死",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "所以你也想要他死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "自己不想死的人，通常也不想要别人死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你若想杀人，就得准备着被杀！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你想要的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "我只想知道一件事",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "这个人是谁，为什么要杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要找的人就是我！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "真的是你要杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "嗯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "那些人都是你找来杀我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你认得我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不认得",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "不认得为什么要杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "艾青呢？她们姐妹是不是被你绑走的？她们的人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你难道一定要我逼你，你才肯开口？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要问的话，我都可以说出来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你为什么不说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在这里我不能说",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "要在什么地方你才能说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "床上",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "床上，你若想睡，就跟我上床",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你好像很懂得看女人",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在你是否已满意？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "抱我到床上去",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不想知道那些事？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "我想",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不想要我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "我想",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既然你想，为什么还不来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "是谁要你这么做的，你为什么要……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_jiao_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "喊叫女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捉贼，快来捉贼！这里有个采花贼",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你是个君子？不是个聪明人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "两样都不是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "也许我只不过是个傻子",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "也许你根本就不是个人",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你知不知道我本来以为你一定会失望的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道，就连我自己，都以为我一定会很失望的",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "但现在你好像并不觉得失望",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那也许只因为我从来都没有真的那么样的盼望过",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "你盼望过什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么都没有，现在我已经很满足",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    }
